{"tid":170450,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"比啲意見 Canon 80d定M5","createTime":"2017-03-24T17:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T14:57:08.000Z","uid":53981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2147d1e3bd6184dec470c2d6c0eabd1eee902b26","tid":170450,"uid":53981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:05:51.000Z","msg":"咁我本身部600d都已經用左4-5年, 最近就想升級。<br />\n<br />\n依家手頭上有Sigma 17-55 f2.8 Tokina 11-16 f2.8 Canon 50 f1.8&nbsp;<br />\n同埋一支好舊嘅垃圾Tamron 18-200天涯鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要去旅行同埋間唔中行山用<br />\n主要影景同埋影下女朋友<br />\n基本上唔會拍片&nbsp;唔影sport唔打雀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我已經起YouTube 睇過好多Reviews但都仲係決定唔到轉唔轉無反<br />\n廢事比人屌 咁我就先講左我自己對兩部機嘅意見 睇下有冇用家可以分享下比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n80d<br />\n-用慣單反手感同control好啲 但係重有時都唔係咁想拎出街 同埋去旅行揹成日有啲辛苦<br />\n<br />\n-手上啲鏡全部用得翻<br />\n<br />\n-對600d黎講都叫做一個大升級<br />\n<br />\n-多鏡選擇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nM5<br />\n<br />\n-機身輕 但係用翻efs鏡加埋adaptor就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(同埋唔知用非Canon鏡對焦會唔會好慢）<br />\n<br />\n-spec同80d基本上一樣 仲平大約1000蚊<br />\n<br />\n-efm冇乜鏡<br />\n<br />\n-evf好似幾正 仲可以同時用touch mon focus&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n-好快冇電<br />\n<br />\n-個on9反mon向下反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-冇weather sealing<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時係諗到咁多"},{"pid":"da52629b960e1a9e7f0eea251e58a0bfee47ef6d","tid":170450,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:07:13.000Z","msg":"直程轉會吧喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725d843431b2d6e372774715d0a7522150939a87","tid":170450,"uid":53981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:07:29.000Z","msg":"btw 暫時唔打算上ff 應該都唔會轉會"},{"pid":"762bf20d5a8fe2d29b242152792c907f46a61243","tid":170450,"uid":53981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直程轉會吧喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSony a6300?"},{"pid":"fc40e48e6234afd10517917c1303263051b3a64d","tid":170450,"uid":76706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:11:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>直程轉會吧喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSony a6300?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nA7 II"},{"pid":"6e478da495d84a28640e011c33999cd3f0292039","tid":170450,"uid":53981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:26:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>直程轉會吧喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSony a6300?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nA7 II</blockquote><br />\n那有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18136c311b4339c3979dfb956aca17c9c3d0850c","tid":170450,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:44:46.000Z","msg":"fuji都好過canon啦"},{"pid":"08a22ce843f7a46e8f6977595a48d7ee1f476f7c","tid":170450,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T18:06:25.000Z","msg":"你兩支大光圏zoom好重, 你上毒氣室試下揾支差唔多重量嘅鏡插落部M5度試下會唔會頭重尾輕到好唔就手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6121d00e932e38eaa5e39b32f7d80a1ef2baa6f","tid":170450,"uid":53981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T18:46:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你兩支大光圏zoom好重, 你上毒氣室試下揾支差唔多重量嘅鏡插落部M5度試下會唔會頭重尾輕到好唔就手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗實會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s