，入左80d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩評價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n畫質提升好多，同focus ，準對有升級感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d3db603abf55634f6f6f8b141a3c1f85ddb77e","tid":170450,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>m5<del> 個evf</del> 廢<br />\n<del>refresh rate</del> 唔好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已協助改正"},{"pid":"a8241df2ad7f5af3d75543239144a34c474cb7f0","tid":170450,"uid":53981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T08:22:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>m5<del> 個evf</del> 廢<br />\n<del>refresh rate</del> 唔好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已協助改正</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eedf166316d3072298937d45abc0c16f2ff9c1e","tid":170450,"uid":56167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T10:10:34.000Z","msg":"用緊 M5 每日放袋跟身<br />\nDefault adapter + 50mm 1.8/f STM <br />\n頭尾啱啱好<br />\n<br />\n其餘 efs10-18, efm15-45<br />\n平時覺得efm 已經夠用，唔點聞相或要求大光圈zoom<br />\n想買 efm 22mm"},{"pid":"a180df96e668e87e22aa8428e655e5f3be462909","tid":170450,"uid":37820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T14:57:08.000Z","msg":"77d都出緊<br />\n可以考慮埋先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n80d+50mm f1.8 stm都唔會重"}]}